start and run through adb

open one terminal
$ npx react-native start



instruction for adb connection

1.connect android phone to pc through usb
2.enable usb debugging and file transfer mode
3.check current local ip of your phone
3.open terminal and enter follwing commands

# For check adb connected or not 
$ adb devices
# for tcp port configuration
$ adb tcpip 5555
# connect the adb through wireless
$ adb connect <mobile_ip[192.168.1.X]>

4.open another terminal
$ npx react-native run-android
